summary: I do some updated color art for my fankids! Please respect my ships, and I’ll respect yours! :) Makoto, Hayate, and...
caption:
I do some updated color art for my fankids! Please respect my ships, and I’ll respect yours! :)

Makoto, Hayate, and Kirika!

Makoto (daughter of Fenneko and Manumaru)

She is age 5 and considers herself a tomboy. She would like to join sports when she’s older, and she greatly enjoys surfing the web. Like her mother she is sarcastic and has a deadpan laugh and a like for mystery. She considers herself very social, and will join her father roughhousing. If you make her angry, she will make you pay and holds a grudge! She loves meat, unlike her mother her favorite food is barbecue chicken!

Hayate (son of Haida and Retsuko)

Age 7. He is an enthusiastic child who from his parents gained a love of music. His classmates think he is “cool”, and he is usually confident and cocky, but he is also a little shy when meeting people for the first time.He is best friends with Makoto. He has a temper that he can keep hidden but he lets out his rage playing on his bass.He grow up with metal and punk music, and his attitude reflects.He has big paws, but he is going to grow into them.

Kirika (daughter of Komiya and Tsunoda)

Age 6. She is spoiled with everything she wants and as such is a little bit of a brat, and is always loving attention. She is enrolled in a private school and ballet lessons so she has a busy schedule and not much time to make friends. She is doted on by her parents, and she loves to pose for pictures. She can act very sweet but really be thinking badly behind your back, and loves sweet desserts. She does not like her tiny horns so covers with a headband.
